  <tr>
   <td colspan="4" class="content">
    <pre>This is directly related to the following SSL problem, caused by me during the
nginx transition:

<a href="mailto:paulproteus@pathi">paulproteus@pathi</a>:/tmp$ wget -O /dev/null <a href="https://openhatch.org/">https://openhatch.org/</a>
--2011-08-20 22:56:29--  <a href="https://openhatch.org/">https://openhatch.org/</a>
Resolving openhatch.org... 74.207.229.254
Connecting to openhatch.org|74.207.229.254|:443... connected.
ERROR: cannot verify openhatch.org’s certificate, issued by “/C=US/O=GeoTrust,
Inc./CN=RapidSSL CA”:
  Unable to locally verify the issuer’s authority.

Fixing it now.</pre>
   </td>
